Status report of Yi Tong Tse on 1/22/99

I was mainly busy with writing code this week.  At this point, the following
items have been done:

    - set up directory structure: basically I reuse the tree structure as
      in RateMux, but added a new directory dpi for the DPI code.

    - set up main program and major task functions: the two new tasks for
      DPI: bufferer Task and switcher Task, are added to the existing tasks
      in RateMux.

    - set up data structures: we try to reuse the existing ones in RateMux
      as much as possible.

